Revision history for Perl module Win32::GUI

1.13 2017-07-26

    * fix for SF#85 Win32::GUI test fail on Win 7 Strawberry Perl 5.24.0.1 and 5.22.2.1
    * fix for SF#84 Win32::GUI does not build on Cygwin if caseinsensitive=0 

1.12 2015-06-03

    * fix for "loadable library and perl binaries are mismatched (got handshake key .., needed ..)" seen at perl-5.22

1.11 2014-11-08

    * fixing Default Window Background Colour (regression)
    * v1.10 intentionally skipped

1.09 2014-11-05

    * tuning POD to be correctly published on metacpan.org and search.cpan.org
    * fix for gcc3 failure http://www.cpantesters.org/cpan/report/af62eb6b-6bfa-1014-83e1-562a373b20f7
    * better handling of deprecated cygwin_conv_to_win32_path() & co.
    * dwData changed from void* to IV
    * tuning pointer casting to properly handle 32/64bit on both win/cygwin platforms
    * fix for -accel failure http://www.cpantesters.org/cpan/report/02fddc46-74e9-1014-b226-8b42afe32da0
    * introducing ENV variables: SKIP_WIN32_GUI_AXWINDOW, SKIP_WIN32_GUI_GRID, SKIP_WIN32_GUI_DIBITMAP
    * fix for strcmpi failure http://www.cpantesters.org/cpan/report/8952733e-6e36-1014-a6c4-79d25cf4dae8

1.08   2014-10-13

    * 64bit cygwin support
    * 64bit MSVC support
    * [IMPORTANT] removed deprecated constants autoloading in Win32::GUI
      'use Win32::GUI' and 'use Win32::GUI()' now works the same (no warnings, no constants)
      'use Win32::GUI qw(CONSTANT_NAME)' still works
    * [IMPORTANT] removed deprecated Win32::GUI::constant()
      use Win32::GUI::Constants::constant() instead
      or  Win32::GUI::_constant() for WIN32__GUI__* constants
    * Win32::GUI::AxWindow + Win32::GUI::DIBitmap disabled on 64bit MSVC (it fails to compile)
    * Under some circumstances ExtUtils::MakeMaker ignores Makefile.PL files in Win32-GUI-* subdirectories
      the failure looks like this: http://www.cpantesters.org/cpan/report/cab5df3f-6c00-1014-ad8f-34fbb365f02c
      renaming these dirs to Win32-GUI_* seems to fix the issue
    * fix for http://sourceforge.net/p/perl-win32-gui/bugs/78/
    * CHANGELOG renamed to Changes + format changed to be compatible with CPAN::Changes::Spec

